== 分佈 ==
''Agaricus subrufescens'' forms fruitbodies singly or in clusters in leaf litter in rich soil, often in domestic habitats.<ref name="isbn0-472-85599-9">{{Cite book|author=Smith, Alexander Hanchett |title=A Field Guide to Western Mushrooms |url=https://archive.org/details/fieldguidetowest0000smit |publisher=University of Michigan Press |location=Ann Arbor, Mich |year=1975 |page=[https://archive.org/details/fieldguidetowest0000smit/page/228 228] |isbn=0-472-85599-9}}{{Page needed|date=August 2010}}</ref>Originally described from the northeastern United States and Canada, it has been found growing in California, Hawaii, Great Britain, the Netherlands, Taiwan, Philippines and Brazil.<ref name="pmid16389952"/>

==安全性==
初步研究顯示巴西蘑菇產品會產生[[肝毒性|肝毒性]]（在一例尝试用蘑菇治疗卵巢癌的患者身上发现），並可能在一些人身上引起[[過敏|過敏]]<ref name=mskcc>{{cite web |title=Agaricus |url=https://www.mskcc.org/cancer-care/integrative-medicine/herbs/agaricus#msk_professional |publisher=Memorial Sloan Kettering Cancer Center |accessdate=21 November 2018 |date=2018 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225050823/https://www.mskcc.org/cancer-care/integrative-medicine/herbs/agaricus#msk_professional |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="sweet">{{cite journal |pmc=4613776|year=2013|last1=Sweet|first1=E. S.|title=Adverse events associated with complementary and alternative medicine use in ovarian cancer patients|journal=Integrative Cancer Therapies|volume=12|issue=6|pages=508–516|last2=Standish|first2=L. J.|last3=Goff|first3=B.|last4=Andersen|first4=M. R.|pmid=23625025|doi=10.1177/1534735413485815}}</ref>。

